messages.message:
[starting a new thread to not spam dept-enginerring]
i’m still seeing the slow db query warning in my local env, even though i’ve set `"db_enable_server_stats": false` (see https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C06FA6A23/p1700259035334659)

is anyone else still seeing this?
I don’t think the changes to `env-local.json` were checked in. So if anyone pulled from master and/or reverted their changes to `env-local.json`, they would be making those expensive queries again.
I merged the PR but I think we will have to ask everyone to do what they did last week (or rebase on master) and restart services. We can ping on the other thread tomorrow during business hours.
